org.firewaterframework.rest
Class Method

java.lang.Object
  org.firewaterframework.rest.Method

public class Method
extends java.lang.Object

This class corresponds to the HTTP METHOD header argument in that protocol. The class provides a number of static properties to define all of the METHODs used by Firewater.
